lead_paragraph: Spain coach Vicente del Bosque is delighted with his side's preparations for the European Championships but was not ready to claim they were short odds to register a third successive triumph at the tournament hosted by France.

headline.print_headline: Del Bosque Confident of Spain's Chances at Euro 2016
